Trump watches press reports about himself and sometimes responds publicly. Often he will try to manipulate reporting about himself. He is said to be very image concious.

Otherwise, Trump is no stranger to coercion and threats, veiled or otherwise:


https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/donald-trump-alter-ego-barron/2016/05/12/02ac99ec-16fe-11e6-aa55-670cabef46e0_story.html
